  "Yes, because the throw force continues after release of ball": "",
  "No, because gravity should point to the right not downward": "",
  "The diagram is incorrect. Once the ball leaves the hand, there is no horizontal force on it (ignoring air resistance). The ball continues horizontally due to inertia, not a force. Only gravity acts on it, pointing downward.": ""
